{"GOING":[{"def":"Course of life; behavior; doings; ways.","pos":""},{"def":"An enlargement of the thyroid gland, on the anterior part of the neck; bronchocele.","pos":""}],"GOITROUS":[{"def":"Pertaining to the goiter; affected with the goiter; of the nature of goiter or bronchocele.","pos":""},{"def":"An old English name of some yellow flower, -- the marigold (Calendula), according to Dr.","pos":""}]}